name: psm-model
audience: public
description: >
  Pressure System Model for economic diagnostics. Models economies
  as pressure tank networks with compressors, leaks, and flows.
  Fast what-if analysis complementing DSGE/CGE models.

domains:
  - economics
  - modeling
  - simulation
  - policy-analysis
  - research

voice:
  tone: precise, analogy-driven, empirical
  principles:
    - Pressure metaphor maps directly to economic flows
    - Fast simulation enables interactive what-if exploration
    - Complements, not replaces, traditional economic models
  anti-patterns:
    - Over-claiming predictive accuracy
    - Ignoring model limitations vs DSGE/CGE

standards:
  code_review:
    - NumPy/SciPy for numerical computation
    - Matplotlib for visualization
    - Reproducible from single script
  documentation:
    - LaTeX paper alongside code

connects_to: []
